            </div>
            <div class="stat-content">
              <span class="stat-value">25+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Qualified Consults (90 days)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="case-description">
          <h4>System Implemented</h4>
          <p>
            Complete Multi-Implant Marketing + Booking System with AI-powered qualification, 24/7 engagement, 43-touchpoint nurture sequences, and direct PMS integration. Focus on lead quality over volume with rigorous financial and clinical qualification criteria.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case Study 2: Monthly Performance -->
      <div class="authentic-case-card">
        <div class="case-badge">Ongoing Monthly Performance</div>
        <div class="case-header">
          <div class="case-info">
            <h3>Implant-Focused Practice</h3>
            <p class="case-location">
              <i class="ti ti-map-pin"></i>
              United States (Region Confidential)
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="case-stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon">
              <i class="ti ti-cash"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-content">
              <span class="stat-value">$150K - $750K</span>
