            Full patient pipeline automation including targeted Google and Facebook campaigns, instant AI + human engagement, smart qualification workflows, automated nurturing, direct calendar scheduling, and case acceptance training. System delivers consistent 10-40 qualified consultations monthly with 75% acceptance rate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================
       EXPECTED RESULTS SECTION
  ============================================ -->
  <section class="expected-results-section">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">
          <i class="ti ti-trending-up"></i>
          What to Expect
        </span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Typical Results from Our System</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          Based on real data from practices using our Multi-Implant Booking System for 90+ days.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="results-timeline">
        
